Package: packetnet
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: Tom Fanning <tom@m0lte.uk>
Depends: adduser, libc6, polkitd | policykit-1
Recommends: python3
Section: hamradio
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/m0lte/packet.net
Description: Packet.NET AX.25 packet-radio node (pdn)
 A modern AX.25 v2.2 packet-radio node host built on .NET. Connected-mode
 sessions over KISS (serial/USB or TCP) and AX.25-over-UDP, with a telnet
 console and an HTTP management surface. Self-contained: bundles its own
 .NET runtime, so no system runtime is required.
